{"tid":497873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會晨跑晨操？","createTime":"2017-12-13T08:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T10:04:41.000Z","uid":158617,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"98f2e0d8c1fec8380c0cbde8d85edacf92db802f","tid":497873,"uid":158617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:51:27.000Z","msg":"最近精神亢奮每日瞓到5點自然醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，的起心肝由夜晚做gym轉做返工前做，5點起身，7點開始gym一個鐘，沖埋個涼之後返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢種生活開始上癮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 停唔到落黎，好享受天未光夜闌人靜，成個城市仲沉睡但係我已經起身運動既感覺，熱血沸騰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲一樣咁享受晨跑晨操？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db1fa89aa739321b8f64c809222aedcfc589b84","tid":497873,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:58:11.000Z","msg":"返工有冇精神左"},{"pid":"a40edd495b78a96eefddaa982aca0b736b5eaef8","tid":497873,"uid":158617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返工有冇精神左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做野集中又精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 工作效率大大提升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47612742b5df92b9cd1106d1f59f6cf684402864","tid":497873,"uid":2966,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:32:36.000Z","msg":"下午食完飯開始會攰到仆街唔想做野"},{"pid":"33a3edf348d105a504f43eb672f19a038826a077","tid":497873,"uid":55914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"想跑返工，但懶仲未實行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a848329