sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都唔會太攰既"},{"pid":"944602e5ffa1a1dc26b1e5a703ec277fe6c0a6cb","tid":497873,"uid":158617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想跑返工，但懶仲未實行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個太癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我跑返工要跑幾個全馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1e9fe35a90f07daaf35021e0a2286c2019909e","tid":497873,"uid":158617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T10:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想精神亢奮, 我都好中意個種太陽岩岩出緊黎, 成個城市仲沉睡緊但我就已經跑緊步個種感覺, 但係我做唔到, 有無咩方法可以達成到? 就咁靠自律自問真係做唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我有夜跑開一直都好想試晨跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係一個女仔好危險，同埋以前每個朝早都冇動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家轉左會做gym，可以book第一堂做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加上瞓唔到咁多，每日都好積極早起晨操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打我地可以互相勉勵，有人督促你應該會易做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}